jc.fog.presentation.commands

Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • jc.fog.presentation.commands.Command
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ForgetPassword, LogoutCommand, ShowAddRegisterCommand, ShowAddRequestCommand, ShowAdminDeleteUserCommand, ShowAdminNewPasswordCommand, ShowAdminUpdateRankCommand, ShowAdminUsersCommand, ShowBillCommand, ShowCarPortCommand, ShowDrawingCommand, ShowLoginCheckCommand, ShowLoginCommand, ShowMaterialsCommand, ShowRegisterCommand, ShowRequestsCommand, ShowSingleMaterialeCommand, ShowUpdateRequestCommand, ShowUserHomeCommand, ShowUserPasswordCommand, ShowUserPasswordUpdate, UnknownCommand

    public abstract class Command
extends Object
    Command class to be extended into specific commands accepted by the front controller. Functionality common to all implementing classes is assembled here. Use static String members to specify the supported commands in the views.
    Author:
    Claus
